<plot>Film based on a Award Winning Novel by Luis Arambilet: El secreto de Neguri (Alfaguara, 2005). The film is a combination (Documentary/Drama), a recount of the story origins, accompanied by two short films based on the original plot. Armando Neguri is a musician that discovers a secret passage under the kitchen sink. The passage opens to a mysterious parallel universe where Neguri can observe the neighbors using sophisticated visors.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?173554</url></doc>
